('w_work_B2_01','KPI','/ˌkeɪ piː ˈaɪ/','noun','핵심성과지표','Key Performance Indicator — a measurable business goal.','Track your {KPIs} monthly.','KPI를 매달 추적하세요.','KPIs','B2','work',2,'KPI dashboard metrics chart'),
