('w_work_B2_03','synergy','/ˈsɪnərdʒi/','noun','시너지','Combined effort producing a greater result.','The merger created real {synergy}.','합병이 진정한 시너지를 만들었어요.','synergy','B2','work',2,'synergy teamwork collaboration merge'),
